quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  113,1,"Say: \"I commit myself to Allah the Creator of the dawn and the incipient gleam"
  113,2,"Counter to the evil generated by the spiritual, the animate and the inanimate among those created by Him, the Supreme"
  113,3,"And counter to an evil process evolving under the umbrella of the night\" or \"to a heavenly body \" if it happens to explode within or beyond one’s sight"
  113,4,And counter to the evil generated by the witches who stand in the way of concord and blow over entangled knots to fan the flow of discord
  113,5,And counter to the evil generated by the envious when he feels envy at the superior advantages of others